criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Individuals with at least 20 permanent teeth in their mouth,

          -  who did not smoke,

          -  who did not have systemic disease other than diabetes were included in the study.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Individuals with any systemic disease other than diabetes that can affect the
             inflammatory conditions;

          -  smokers;

          -  pregnant or lactating;

          -  those using antibiotics or anti-inflammatory drugs;

          -  those who had received periodontal treatment in the last six months were excluded from
             the study.
